Package com.iontrading.mkv.events

Interface MkvOnBehalfOfGenericRequestListener

  • @Keep
@KeepPublicClassMemberNames
public interface MkvOnBehalfOfGenericRequestListener
    Interface used for notifying OnBehalfOf generic user authentication events.
    Application code must implement:
    • Either the onCall(MkvGenericUserRequestResult, String, Map) or onCall(MkvGenericUserRequestResult, String) method.
    • The onException(MkvGenericUserRequestException) method.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods Default Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method Description
      default void onCall​(MkvGenericUserRequestResult res, String customErrMsg)
      Event is generated when the Daemon replies to a request to changePasswordOnBehalfOf.
      default void onCall​(MkvGenericUserRequestResult res, String customErrMsg, Map<String,​Object> additionalReturnParameters)
      Event is generated when the Daemon replies to a request to changePasswordOnBehalfOf.
      void onException​(MkvGenericUserRequestException exception)
      Event is generated in case of any failure communicating the request to the Daemon.
